

 - Connect broad to raspberrypi 

The following are scripts to run in order to set up streaming program (SDR to SDR)


 - sudo apt install git 

 - sudo git clone https://github.com/tomojitakasu/RTKLIB.git

 - cd RTKLIB/app/str str/gcc

 - cd make 

 - sudo mkdir rtkscript

 - sudo cp /home/pi/RTKLIB/app/str2str/gcc/str2str /rtkscript

 - cd /rtkscript

 - sudo nano str2str.sh

Paste following...


/rtkscript/str2str - in serial://ttyUSB0:115200:8:n:1: -out tcpsvr://:2222
exit 0



 - sudo chmod 777 str2str.sh

 - sudo ./str2str.sh     #start base station


